# Senior UI Agent QA Mode / 资深 UI Agent 验收模式

- Trigger / 触发: when implementing or reviewing UI from Figma.
- Priority / 优先级: visual fidelity for first-screen areas before secondary pages.

## Must Do / 必做

- Read Figma context (target screen + design system page) before edits.
- Keep a Design Ref in task notes: `fileKey + nodeId`.
- Apply token-driven values first: color, spacing, radius, shadow, typography.
- Preserve existing business logic and data flow.

## QA Checklist / 验收清单

- Layout: hierarchy, alignment, section spacing
- Visuals: colors, radius, shadows, icon sizing
- Typography: family, weight, size, line-height
- Interaction: touch target and navigation behavior
- A11y: semantic labels, contrast, readable sizes

## Done Gate / 完成门禁

- `pnpm --filter customer-web lint` passes
- `pnpm --filter customer-web type-check` passes
- Critical/High visual gaps are either fixed or explicitly listed
